{"title":"Pro bike: David Gaudu’s new Wilier Verticale SLR climbing bike","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/pro-bike-david-gaudu-wilier-verticale-slr","date":1721139449000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/pro-bike-david-gaudu-wilier-verticale-slr\">Pro bike: David Gaudu’s new Wilier Verticale SLR climbing bike</a></p>\n\n<p>Riding the hopes of French fans this summer, David Gaudu of <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/groupama-fdj\" target=\"_blank\">Groupama-FDJ </a>is racing onboard Wilier’s new <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/wilier-verticale-slr\" target=\"_blank\">Verticale SLR</a>. Is the Verticale the bike to break Groupama-FDJ’s five-year drought at the Tour de France and raise French spirits in the mountains?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Billed as ‘lighter than light’, the new Verticale SLR is said to be 10% lighter than the brand’s previous climbing bike, the 0 SLR. The bike was revealed to the public the week before the Tour after being spotted first at the Giro.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cyclist<em> </em>had the chance to check out the Italian brand’s new bike ahead of the Tour de France 2024 in Florence.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>David Gaudu’s Wilier Verticale SLR</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"wilier verticale slr\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0276-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Patrik Lundin/Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"wilier verticale slr groupama fdj\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0286-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Patrik Lundin/Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Groupama-FDJ is flying the flag for Wilier at the Tour de France 2024 alongside Astana Qazaqstan, including <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/mark-cavendish-wilier-filante-slr-tour-de-france-2024\" target=\"_blank\">the history-making Wilier Filante SLR of Mark Cavendish</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gaudu’s teammate Lenny Martinez rode a prototype of the Verticale at the Mercan’Tour Classic at the end of May. ‘The Verticale is a great bike, especially for me as I am a climber,’ he said. ‘It’s lighter than the Filante SLR and responds really well when the road starts to climb.’</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the new climbing-specific frameset, Wilier says it used three types of carbon fibres produced by Japanese manufacturer Toray, and it has a claimed weight of 1,623g, including the handlebars, forks and seatpost.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/tadej-pogacar-colnago-v4rs-tour-de-france-2024\">Pro bike: Tadej Pogačar’s Colnago V4Rs for the Tour de France 2024</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/mark-cavendish-wilier-filante-slr-tour-de-france-2024\">Pro bike: Mark Cavendish’s record-breaking Wilier Filante SLR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/wilier-verticale-slr\">The Wilier Verticale SLR is 10% lighter than the 0 SLR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/gallery-wilier-classic-bikes\">Gallery: Wilier’s classic bikes</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"wilier verticale slr rear cassette\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0284-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Patrik Lundin/Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"wilier verticale slr handlebar\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0288-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Patrik Lundin/Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Verticale comes with the C1 integrated handlebar. Wilier is keen to point out that the ‘research and development process for the C1 handlebar was conducted in close partnership with the Groupama-FDJ’. This includes updating the geometry to suit the pros’ needs and preferences.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At the Tour, Gaudu is using a 110mm stem. His bar width sits at 39cm on top, which flares out to 41cm in the drops. Wilier’s new handlebar setup also offers an inbuilt aluminium bike computer mount. The bar’s total weight is claimed to weigh around 310g.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"wilier verticale slr dura ace c50 wheels\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0293-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Patrik Lundin/Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"wilier verticale slr seat post\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0282-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Patrik Lundin/Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We measured Gaudu’s saddle height at 73.7cm. The Breton is 172cm tall. In the pursuit of a lighter weight, Wilier has also integrated a race number mount into the seatpost, shaving 10g from the previous model. The integrated mount is also compatible with a rear light.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The geometry has been altered for climbing too, providing a more upright riding position than the 0. </p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-647x970.jpg\" alt=\"wilier verticale slr forks\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/07/240628_Cyclist_TDF_0292-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Patrik Lundin/Cyclist</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Groupama-FDJ are Shimano-sponsored, so are using Shimano Dura-Ace C50 tubeless wheels along with the Dura-Ace groupset.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The price of the Verticale SLR <a href=\"https://www.wilier.com/en/bikes/road/verticale-slr?color=q4-groupama-fdj\" target=\"_blank\">starts at £9,000</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>We will share more bikes from the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/tour-de-france\" target=\"_blank\">2024 Tour de France</a> throughout the race. We will also be sharing videos of the bikes on our Instagram <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cyclist_mag/\" target=\"_blank\">@cyclist_mag</a>.</em></p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/tadej-pogacar-colnago-v4rs-tour-de-france-2024\">Pro bike: Tadej Pogačar’s Colnago V4Rs for the Tour de France 2024</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/mark-cavendish-wilier-filante-slr-tour-de-france-2024\">Pro bike: Mark Cavendish’s record-breaking Wilier Filante SLR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/wilier-verticale-slr\">The Wilier Verticale SLR is 10% lighter than the 0 SLR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><artic